psalm.text:
[[Ps 59,2]]Rescue me from my enemies, O my God; 
from my adversaries defend me.
[[Ps 59,3]]Rescue me from evildoers; 
from bloodthirsty men save me.

[[Ps 59,4]]For behold, they lie in wait for my life; 
mighty men come together against me, 
not for any offense or sin of mine, O LORD.

[[Ps 59,10]]O my strength! for you I watch; 
for you, O God, are my stronghold,
[[Ps 59,11]]As for my God, may his mercy go before me; 
may he show me the fall of my foes.

[[Ps 59,17]]But I will sing of your strength 
and revel at dawn in your mercy; 
you have been my stronghold, 
my refuge in the day of distress.

[[Ps 59,18]]O my strength! your praise will I sing; 
for you, O God, are my stronghold, 
my merciful God!
